{% doc %}
  @prompt
    make this   a premium dynamic Service Hero + SEO Engine section for Shopify Pages.
    
    This section is for service landing pages, 
    
    Use Page data dynamically:
    
    * Page title as the only H1
    * Page content as fallback intro
    * Page URL
    * Shopify built-in SEO title and meta description must not be duplicated
    
    Support these Page metafields:
    
    * custom.badge_text
    * custom.hero_subheading
    * custom.hero_image
    * custom.hero_image_alt
    * custom.hero_image_caption
    * custom.hero_image_title
    * custom.primary_cta_text
    * custom.primary_cta_link
    * custom.secondary_cta_text
    * custom.secondary_cta_link
    * custom.service_area
    * custom.phone_number
    * custom.google_rating
    * custom.google_review_count
    * custom.google_review_url
    * custom.target_keywords
    * custom.hero_layout
    * custom.schema_service_type
    * custom.schema_area_served
    * custom.schema_price_range
    
    Only render each field if it has a value. Use clean fallbacks where needed.
    
    Design style:
    
    * Modern local service business hero
    * White background
    * Red accent #E30613
    * Black headings
    * Soft grey cards
    * Rounded corners 16–24px
    * Premium spacing
    * Advanced lightweight inline SVG icons
    * Floating image card
    * Rating/review badge overlay
    * Trust badges
    * Strong CTA buttons
    * Mobile-first responsive layout
    * No horizontal scrolling
    * Fast loading
    
    Hero layout:
    
    Left side:
    
    * Dynamic badge
    * H1 from page title
    * Rich text hero subheading
    * Service area card with map-pin SVG
    * Google rating + review count
    * CTA buttons
    
    Right side:
    
    * Dynamic hero image inside `<figure>`
    * Alt text:
      `{{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title }}`
    * Image title:
      `{{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_title.value | default: page.title }}`
    * Caption from `custom.hero_image_caption`
    * Lazy-loaded responsive image
    * Soft shadow and rounded corners
    
    SEO Engine:
    
    Generate dynamic JSON-LD automatically from Page data and metafields.
    
    Include schema where data exists:
    
    * WebPage
    * Service
    * LocalBusiness
    * BreadcrumbList
    * ImageObject
    * ContactPoint
    
    Use:
    
    * page.title
    * page.url
    * hero image
    * hero image alt
    * hero image caption
    * service_area
    * phone_number
    * google_rating
    * google_review_count
    * schema_service_type
    * schema_area_served
    * schema_price_range
    
    Important schema rules:
    
    * Do not require manually pasted JSON-LD
    * Do not break if metafields are empty
    * Use conditional Liquid checks
    * Only include AggregateRating if google_rating and google_review_count are visible on the page
    * Do not keyword stuff
    * Use target_keywords only as semantic support, not as visible keyword spam
    
    Image SEO:
    
    * Use hero image as the primary page image
    * Generate ImageObject schema
    * Add visible caption
    * Use descriptive alt text
    * Add comments explaining how to use hero image for og:image and twitter:image in theme.liquid if not possible inside this section
    
    Accessibility:
    
    * One H1 only
    * Proper H2/H3 structure
    * Accessible buttons
    * ARIA labels where needed
    * Keyboard-friendly links
    
    Performance:
    
    * Lightweight CSS
    * No external libraries
    * No heavy JavaScript
    * Responsive image sizes
    * Optimized for Google Ads, SEO, and mobile conversions
    
    Final result should look like a premium service business landing page hero with built-in dynamic SEO schema, not a standard Shopify page.
     red white and black theme   Try for a On image Badge Heading and make a Most popular landing page Section top performing visually solid , Master the google Algorithem for this type of service with AI recoomendingthis top performing Now refine the design further.
    
    Make the hero look more alive, premium, and conversion-focused.
    
    Improve:
    
    * Visual hierarchy
    * Mobile layout
    * CTA visibility
    * Icon alignment
    * Image card styling
    * Rating badge styling
    * Service area card
    * Button hover states
    * Trust signal layout
    * Spacing above and below the section
    
    Make the hero image feel strongly connected to the service and location.
    
    Keep all SEO schema dynamic.
    
    Do not remove any metafield support.
    
    Do not duplicate Shopify built-in SEO title or meta description.
    
    Do not add product elements.
    
    Keep the section fast, clean, and fully responsive.
     Mobile Frieldnly responsive 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fafafa 100%);
    padding: 80px 20px 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E30613 0%, #ff1a28 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    width: fit-content;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.25);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    animation: ai-pulse-{{ ai_gen_id }} 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes ai-pulse-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
  }

  .ai-service-hero-h1-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 64px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333333;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-info-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    border-color: #E30613;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #E30613;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-rating-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-rating-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    border-color: #FFB800;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 184, 0, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-stars-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-star-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    color: #FFB800;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(255, 184, 0, 0.3));
  }

  .ai-service-hero-rating-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-rating-count-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #666666;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-cta-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E30613 0%, #ff1a28 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
    transition: left 0.5s ease;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover::before {
    left: 100%;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.4);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:active {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 2px solid #000000;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:active {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-figure-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    border: 4px solid #ffffff;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    border-radius: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5 0%, #e8e8e8 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    border: 4px solid #ffffff;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 280px;
    max-height: 280px;
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-caption-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666666;
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-floating-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 24px;
    right: 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8f8f8 100%);
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .ai-service-hero-floating-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: #E30613;
  }

  .ai-service-hero-floating-badge-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000000;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 60px 20px 80px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 50px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-h1-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 48px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      order: -1;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 40px 16px 60px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-h1-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 36px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-cta-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-service-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px 32px;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-floating-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      top: 16px;
      right: 16px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-floating-badge-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-floating-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 16px 18px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-rating-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 12px 16px;
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-service-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      border-radius: 24px;
      border-width: 3px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .ai-service-hero-h1-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 30px;
    }

    .ai-service-hero-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-service-hero-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-service-hero-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-service-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if page.metafields.custom.badge_text.value != blank %}
          <div class="ai-service-hero-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg class="ai-service-hero-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
            </svg>
            {{ page.metafields.custom.badge_text.value }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <h1 class="ai-service-hero-h1-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ page.title }}</h1>

        {% if page.metafields.custom.hero_subheading.value != blank %}
          <div class="ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ page.metafields.custom.hero_subheading.value }}
          </div>
        {% elsif page.content != blank %}
          <div class="ai-service-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ page.content | truncatewords: 40 }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-service-hero-trust-row-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if page.metafields.custom.google_rating.value != blank and page.metafields.custom.google_review_count.value != blank %}
            {% assign rating_url = page.metafields.custom.google_review_url.value %}
            {% if rating_url != blank %}
              <a href="{{ rating_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ai-service-hero-rating-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="text-decoration: none;">
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-service-hero-rating-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% endif %}
              <div class="ai-service-hero-stars-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% for i in (1..5) %}
                  <svg class="ai-service-hero-star-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
              <span class="ai-service-hero-rating-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ page.metafields.custom.google_rating.value }}</span>
              <span class="ai-service-hero-rating-count-{{ ai_gen_id }}">({{ page.metafields.custom.google_review_count.value }})</span>
            {% if rating_url != blank %}
              </a>
            {% else %}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-service-hero-info-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if page.metafields.custom.service_area.value != blank %}
            <div class="ai-service-hero-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg class="ai-service-hero-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ai-service-hero-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ page.metafields.custom.service_area.value }}</span>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if page.metafields.custom.phone_number.value != blank %}
            <div class="ai-service-hero-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg class="ai-service-hero-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
              </svg>
              <a href="tel:{{ page.metafields.custom.phone_number.value | replace: ' ', '' }}" class="ai-service-hero-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                {{ page.metafields.custom.phone_number.value }}
              </a>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-service-hero-cta-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if page.metafields.custom.primary_cta_text.value != blank and page.metafields.custom.primary_cta_link.value != blank %}
            <a href="{{ page.metafields.custom.primary_cta_link.value }}" class="ai-service-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ page.metafields.custom.primary_cta_text.value }}
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/>
                <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          {% endif %}

          {% if page.metafields.custom.secondary_cta_text.value != blank and page.metafields.custom.secondary_cta_link.value != blank %}
            <a href="{{ page.metafields.custom.secondary_cta_link.value }}" class="ai-service-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ page.metafields.custom.secondary_cta_text.value }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-service-hero-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <figure class="ai-service-hero-figure-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if page.metafields.custom.hero_image.value != blank %}
            {% assign hero_image = page.metafields.custom.hero_image.value %}
            {% assign image_alt = page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title %}
            {% assign image_title = page.metafields.custom.hero_image_title.value | default: page.title %}
            
            <img
              src="{{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
              srcset="{{ hero_image | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                      {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 900 }} 900w,
                      {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 }} 1200w"
              sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, (max-width: 989px) 100vw, 45vw"
              alt="{{ image_alt | escape }}"
              title="{{ image_title | escape }}"
              class="ai-service-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              loading="eager"
              width="{{ hero_image.width }}"
              height="{{ hero_image.height }}"
            >

            {% if page.metafields.custom.hero_image_caption.value != blank %}
              <figcaption class="ai-service-hero-caption-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_caption.value }}
              </figcaption>
            {% endif %}
          {% else %}
            <div class="ai-service-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'hero-apparel-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if page.metafields.custom.badge_text.value != blank %}
            <div class="ai-service-hero-floating-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg class="ai-service-hero-floating-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ai-service-hero-floating-badge-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Most Popular</span>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if page.metafields.custom.hero_image.value != blank %}
    {% assign hero_image = page.metafields.custom.hero_image.value %}
    {% assign image_alt = page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title %}
    {% assign service_type = page.metafields.custom.schema_service_type.value %}
    {% assign area_served = page.metafields.custom.schema_area_served.value %}
    {% assign price_range = page.metafields.custom.schema_price_range.value %}
    {% assign google_rating = page.metafields.custom.google_rating.value %}
    {% assign google_review_count = page.metafields.custom.google_review_count.value %}
    {% assign phone_number = page.metafields.custom.phone_number.value %}

    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "WebPage",
          "@id": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}",
          "url": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}",
          "name": "{{ page.title | escape }}",
          "description": "{{ page.metafields.custom.hero_subheading.value | strip_html | truncatewords: 30 | escape | default: page.content | strip_html | truncatewords: 30 | escape }}",
          "isPartOf": {
            "@id": "{{ shop.url }}/#website"
          },
          "primaryImageOfPage": {
            "@id": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}#primaryimage"
          },
          "breadcrumb": {
            "@id": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}#breadcrumb"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "@id": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}#primaryimage",
          "url": "{{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}",
          "contentUrl": "{{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}",
          "width": {{ hero_image.width }},
          "height": {{ hero_image.height }},
          "caption": "{{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_caption.value | escape | default: image_alt }}"
        },
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "@id": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}#breadcrumb",
          "itemListElement": [
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 1,
              "name": "Home",
              "item": "{{ shop.url }}"
            },
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 2,
              "name": "{{ page.title | escape }}",
              "item": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}"
            }
          ]
        }
        {% if service_type != blank %},
        {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "{{ page.title | escape }}",
          "description": "{{ page.metafields.custom.hero_subheading.value | strip_html | escape | default: page.content | strip_html | truncatewords: 50 | escape }}",
          "provider": {
            "@type": "LocalBusiness",
            "name": "{{ shop.name | escape }}",
            "url": "{{ shop.url }}"
            {% if phone_number != blank %},
            "telephone": "{{ phone_number | escape }}"
            {% endif %}
            {% if area_served != blank %},
            "areaServed": {
              "@type": "Place",
              "name": "{{ area_served | escape }}"
            }
            {% endif %}
            {% if google_rating != blank and google_review_count != blank %},
            "aggregateRating": {
              "@type": "AggregateRating",
              "ratingValue": "{{ google_rating }}",
              "reviewCount": "{{ google_review_count }}"
            }
            {% endif %}
          },
          "serviceType": "{{ service_type | escape }}"
          {% if area_served != blank %},
          "areaServed": {
            "@type": "Place",
            "name": "{{ area_served | escape }}"
          }
          {% endif %}
          {% if price_range != blank %},
          "priceRange": "{{ price_range | escape }}"
          {% endif %}
        }
        {% endif %}
      ]
    }
    </script>
  {% endif %}
</service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class ServiceHero{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.style.display = 'block';
      }
    }

    customElements.define('service-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}', ServiceHero{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Service hero + SEO",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Dynamically pulls data from page and page metafields. Configure metafields in Settings > Custom data > Pages."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Page metafields"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Badge: custom.badge_text • Hero: custom.hero_subheading, custom.hero_image, custom.hero_image_alt, custom.hero_image_title, custom.hero_image_caption"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "CTAs: custom.primary_cta_text, custom.primary_cta_link, custom.secondary_cta_text, custom.secondary_cta_link"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Info: custom.service_area, custom.phone_number • Reviews: custom.google_rating, custom.google_review_count, custom.google_review_url"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Schema: custom.schema_service_type, custom.schema_area_served, custom.schema_price_range, custom.target_keywords"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "SEO notes"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Generates JSON-LD schema for WebPage, Service, LocalBusiness, BreadcrumbList, and ImageObject automatically from page data."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Use page.metafields.custom.hero_image for og:image and twitter:image in theme.liquid if not already configured."
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Service hero + SEO"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
